annotationA: Wing morphogenesis defect, isoform A; Receptor binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: imaginal disc-derived wing morphogenesis
annotationB: Gemin3, isoform A; Gemin3 is an RNA helicase and a member of the SMN-Gemins complex. It is a component of the cytoplasmic U snRNP body and nuclear gems. It is required in the motor system for viability, neuromuscular junction development and motor behaviour
